  <entry>
    <title>nSumTarget问题模板</title>
    <url>/2022/03/30/nSumTarget%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><blockquote>
<p>nSumTarget问题为leetcode中常见的求数组中某几个数之和定于固定值的问题。一般形式为给定数组<code>nums</code>，求数组中<code>n</code>个数之和等于<code>target</code>，返回这<code>n</code>个数的索引、值、和、差值等情况。笔者总结了nSumTarget模板，可以解决求任意<code>n</code>个数等于(接近于)任意<code>target</code>的问题。</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="适用场景"><a href="#适用场景" class="headerlink" title="适用场景"></a>适用场景</h2><p>求数组内<code>n</code>个数之和等于(最接近于)<code>target</code>的数，或求数组内<code>n</code>个数之和最小值(最大值)。</p>
<h2 id="基本思路"><a href="#基本思路" class="headerlink" title="基本思路"></a>基本思路</h2><p>排序+双指针+递归调用，先对数组进行升序排序，然后将<code>n</code>个数求和问题转化为2个数求和问题，用双指针解决两个数求和问题。</p>
<h2 id="注意点"><a href="#注意点" class="headerlink" title="注意点"></a>注意点</h2><ol>
<li><p>跳过所有重复的元素： <code>while (lo &lt; hi &amp;&amp; nums[lo] == left) lo++；while (lo &lt; hi &amp;&amp; nums[hi] == right) hi--;</code>(在找到一个结果后，也应该跳过所有重复项)</p>
</li>
<li><p>在<code>twoSum</code>子问题解决后，需要将当前的元素也push进去，即<code>tuple.push_back(nums[i])</code>;</p>
</li>
<li><p>在一个结果找到后，需要跳过和当前数字重复的情况，否则会出现重复结果;<code>while (i &lt; sz - 1 &amp;&amp; nums[i] == nums[i + 1]) i++;</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>记得每次调用从<code>start</code>开始，不是0开始，否则会出现重复。</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="模板"><a href="#模板" class="headerlink" title="模板"></a>模板</h2><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">//针对nums数组中，求n个数之和为target，起始点为start</span></span><br><span class="line">nums.<span class="title function_">sort</span>(<span class="function">(<span class="params">a,b</span>)=&gt;</span>a-b);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> <span class="title function_">nSumTarget</span>=(<span class="params">nums,n,start,target</span>)=&gt;&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">const</span> sz = nums.<span class="property">length</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">let</span> res = [];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n&lt; <span class="number">2</span> || sz&lt;n)<span class="keyword">return</span> res;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n===<span class="number">2</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> lo = start,hi = sz-<span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(lo&lt;hi)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">let</span> sum = nums[lo]+nums[hi];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">let</span> left = nums[lo],right = nums[hi];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(sum&lt;target)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span>(lo&lt;hi &amp;&amp; nums[lo]===left)lo++;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span>(sum&gt;target)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span>(lo&lt;hi &amp;&amp; nums[hi]===right)hi--;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                res.<span class="title function_">push</span>([nums[lo],nums[hi]]);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span>(lo&lt;hi &amp;&amp; nums[lo]===left)lo++;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">while</span>(lo&lt;hi &amp;&amp; nums[hi]===right)hi--;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">let</span> i=start;i&lt;sz;i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">let</span> sub = <span class="title function_">nSumTarget</span>(nums,n-<span class="number">1</span>,i+<span class="number">1</span>,target-nums[i]);</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">for</span>(arr <span class="keyword">of</span> sub)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                arr.<span class="title function_">push</span>(nums[i]);</span><br><span class="line">                res.<span class="title function_">push</span>(arr);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">while</span> (i &lt; sz - <span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; nums[i] == nums[i + <span class="number">1</span>]) i++;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> res;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="相关题目"><a href="#相关题目" class="headerlink" title="相关题目"></a>相关题目</h2><ul>
<li><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/3sum/">15. 三数之和</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/3sum-closest/">16. 最接近的三数之和</a></p>
</li>
<li><p><a href="https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/4sum/">18. 四数之和</a></p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="参考"><a href="#参考" class="headerlink" title="参考"></a>参考</h2><ul>
<li><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/fSyJVvggxHq28a0SdmZm6Q">一个函数秒杀 2Sum 3Sum 4Sum 问题</a></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
