  <entry>
    <title>手写实现mustache模板引擎</title>
    <url>/2022/03/30/%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0mustache%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><blockquote>
<p>模板引擎是将数据要变为视图最优雅的解决方案，历史上出现过多种多样的模板技术，其本质都是将模文件和数据通过模板引擎生成最终的HTML代码。mustach是JavaScript中一种没有逻辑的模板语法，它可以应用在HTML、配置文化和源代码等任意地方。它通过使用散列或对象中提供的值在模板中展开标记来工作。</p>
</blockquote>
<span id="more"></span>

<h3 id="历史上的模板技术"><a href="#历史上的模板技术" class="headerlink" title="历史上的模板技术"></a>历史上的模板技术</h3><ul>
<li>纯DOM法： 非常笨拙，没有实战价值</li>
<li>数组join法： 曾几何时非常流行，是曾经的前端必会知识</li>
<li>ES6的反引号法： ES6中新增的<code>$&#123;a&#125;</code>语法糖，很好用</li>
<li>模板引擎： 解决数据变为视图的最优雅的方法</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="mustache使用"><a href="#mustache使用" class="headerlink" title="mustache使用"></a>mustache使用</h2><p>mustache是”胡子”的意思，因为它的嵌入标记<code>&#123;&#123;&#125;&#125;`非常像胡子。`&#123;&#123;&#125;&#125;</code>的语法也被vue所沿用。</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title class_">Mustache</span>.<span class="title function_">render</span>(templateStr,<span class="title class_">Data</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li>templateStr : 模板字符串；</li>
<li>Data：需要嵌入模板字符串的数据。</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="mustache实现原理"><a href="#mustache实现原理" class="headerlink" title="mustache实现原理"></a>mustache实现原理</h2><h3 id="什么是tokens？"><a href="#什么是tokens？" class="headerlink" title="什么是tokens？"></a>什么是tokens？</h3><ul>
<li>tokens是一个JavaScript的嵌套数组，说白了，就是模板字符串的JavaScript表示；</li>
<li>它是”抽象语法树“、”虚拟节点“等等的开山鼻祖，相当于编译原理中，解析的词法分析结果；</li>
<li>tokens也会产生嵌套的情况。</li>
</ul>
<p>例如，<code>&lt;h1&gt;我买了一辆&#123;&#123;thing&#125;&#125;,心情好&#123;&#123;mood&#125;&#125;啊&lt;/h1&gt;</code>会被解析程如下的tokens:</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>,  <span class="string">&quot;&lt; h1 &gt;我买了一辆&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>,  ”thing“],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>,  <span class="string">&quot;,心情好&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;name&quot;</span>,  ”mood“],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>,  <span class="string">&quot;W&lt; /h1 &gt;&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="mustach解析过程"><a href="#mustach解析过程" class="headerlink" title="mustach解析过程"></a>mustach解析过程</h3><ul>
<li>将模板字符串编译程tokens形式；</li>
<li>将tokens于数据结合，解析程dom字符串。</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="/2022/03/30/%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0mustache%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/mustache.jpg" alt="mustache模板解析过程"></p>
<h2 id="手写实现mustache库"><a href="#手写实现mustache库" class="headerlink" title="手写实现mustache库"></a>手写实现mustache库</h2><h3 id="开发环境"><a href="#开发环境" class="headerlink" title="开发环境"></a>开发环境</h3><ul>
<li><p>模板化打包工具<code>webpack</code>(<code>webpack-dev-server</code>)、<code>rollyp</code>、<code>Parcel</code>等</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>mustache</code>官方库使用<code>rollup</code>进行模块化打包，而本文采用<code>webpack</code>进行模块化打包，这是因为<code>webpack</code>能让我们更方便地在浏览器中（而不是<code>nodejs</code>环境中）实时调试</p>
</li>
<li><p>生成库是<code>UMD</code>的，既可以在<code>nodejs</code>环境中使用，也可以在浏览器环境中使用</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="主要函数介绍"><a href="#主要函数介绍" class="headerlink" title="主要函数介绍"></a>主要函数介绍</h3><ul>
<li><p><code>index.js</code> ：主入口（包含测试案例）</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>lookup.js</code> ：寻找对象中指定的值</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>nestedTokens.js</code>： 将一维 tokens 折叠为多维 tokens</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>parseTemplateTokens.js </code>：将 template 字符串转换为 token</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>parseTokens.js</code> ：解析循环的 tokens</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>renderTemplate.js</code>： 获得最终的 template 和 data 结合的 DOM 字符串</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>Scanner.js</code> ：Scanner 类对模板字符串进行扫描</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 id="实现Scanner类"><a href="#实现Scanner类" class="headerlink" title="实现Scanner类"></a>实现Scanner类</h3><p><code>Scanner</code>类即一个扫描器，用来扫描模板字符串，有两个属性和三个方法：</p>
<ul>
<li><p><code>pos</code>：记录字符串当前正被扫描的位置</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>tail</code>：记录当前指针及当前指针之后的位置的所有字符串</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>scanUntil(stopTag)</code>：扫描模板字符串，直到遇见第一个<code>stopTag</code>结束，返回扫描过的字符串，此时调用<code>scan()</code>跳过<code>stopTag</code></p>
</li>
<li><p><code>scan()</code>：让指针跳过<code>stopTag</code></p>
</li>
<li><p><code>eos()</code>：判断当前字符串是否扫描完毕</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    扫描器类</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">Scanner</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">constructor</span>(<span class="params">templeteStr</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 将模板字符串绑定实例对象</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">templeteStr</span> = templeteStr;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 指针</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span> = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 尾巴，一开始就是模板字符原文,包括指针在内</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">tail</span> = templeteStr;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 走过指定内容，无返回值</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">scan</span>(<span class="params">tag</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">tail</span>.<span class="title function_">indexOf</span>(tag) == <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// tag有多长，就让指针后移多少位</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span> += tag.<span class="property">length</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 尾巴也同时变</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">tail</span> = <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">templeteStr</span>.<span class="title function_">substring</span>(<span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 让指针进行扫描，直到遇见指定内容(stopTag)结束，并且能够返回结束之前路过的文字</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">scanUtil</span>(<span class="params">stopTag</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 记录以下执行本方法时pos的值</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">const</span> pos_backup = <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 当尾巴的开头不是stopTag，就说明还没有扫描到指定内容</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 写&amp;&amp;很有必要,防止找不到，那么寻找到最后也要停下来</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (!<span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="title function_">eos</span>() &amp;&amp; <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">tail</span>.<span class="title function_">indexOf</span>(stopTag) != <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span>++;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 改变尾巴为从当前指针这个字符开始，到最后的全部字符</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">tail</span> = <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">templeteStr</span>.<span class="title function_">substring</span>(<span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">templeteStr</span>.<span class="title function_">substring</span>(pos_backup, <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 指针是否结束，返回布尔值,end of string</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="title function_">eos</span>(<span class="params"></span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">pos</span> &gt;= <span class="variable language_">this</span>.<span class="property">templeteStr</span>.<span class="property">length</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="实现ParseTemplateToTokens-templeteStr-函数"><a href="#实现ParseTemplateToTokens-templeteStr-函数" class="headerlink" title="实现ParseTemplateToTokens(templeteStr)函数"></a>实现ParseTemplateToTokens(templeteStr)函数</h3><p><code>ParseTemplateToTokens</code>的作用是将模板字符串变为tokens，过程中用到了上述的<code>Scanner</code>类和<code>nestToken</code>类（后文介绍），有三个属性：</p>
<ul>
<li><p><code>tokens</code>：存储<code>tokens</code>结果</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>scanner</code>：用于扫描字符串，跳过结束关键字</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>words</code>：用来保存<code>scaner</code>类扫描过的文字，在合适的地方将文字存入tokens数组</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> <span class="title class_">Scnner</span> <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;./Scanner.js&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> nestTokens <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&#x27;./nestToken.js&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    将模板字符串变为tokens数组</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">parseTemplateToTokens</span>(<span class="params">templeteStr</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> tokens = [];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 创建扫描器</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> scanner = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="title class_">Scnner</span>(templeteStr);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> words;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 让扫描器工作</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> (!scanner.<span class="title function_">eos</span>()) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 收集开始标记出现之前的文字</span></span><br><span class="line">        words = scanner.<span class="title function_">scanUtil</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#123;&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (words != <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 将文字存进tokens数组</span></span><br><span class="line">            tokens.<span class="title function_">push</span>([<span class="string">&#x27;text&#x27;</span>, words]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 扫描大括号</span></span><br><span class="line">        scanner.<span class="title function_">scan</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#123;&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 收集结束标记出现之前的文字</span></span><br><span class="line">        words = scanner.<span class="title function_">scanUtil</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (words != <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// words是&#123;&#123;&#125;&#125;中间的东西,判断以下首字符</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (words[<span class="number">0</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;#&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 将文字存进tokens数组,从下标为1的项开始存,下标为0是#</span></span><br><span class="line">                tokens.<span class="title function_">push</span>([<span class="string">&#x27;#&#x27;</span>, words.<span class="title function_">substring</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (words[<span class="number">0</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 将文字存进tokens数组,从下标为1的项开始存,下标为0是/</span></span><br><span class="line">                tokens.<span class="title function_">push</span>([<span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>, words.<span class="title function_">substring</span>(<span class="number">1</span>)]);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 将文字存进tokens数组</span></span><br><span class="line">                tokens.<span class="title function_">push</span>([<span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>, words]);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 扫描大括号</span></span><br><span class="line">        scanner.<span class="title function_">scan</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;&#125;&#125;&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 返回折叠的tokens</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="title function_">nestTokens</span>(tokens);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="实现nestTokens-函数"><a href="#实现nestTokens-函数" class="headerlink" title="实现nestTokens()函数"></a>实现nestTokens()函数</h3><ul>
<li><p>如上节所述，在遇到<code>#</code>字符时，需要进行嵌套存储。<code>nestTokens</code>类用于将一个未嵌套过的<code>tokens</code>处理成嵌套后的<code>nestedTokens</code>返回。</p>
</li>
<li><p>这里，我们需要将#和/之间的字符串放入到当前<code>token</code>数组的第三项，作为它的嵌套项(<code>tokens</code>数组包含若干个<code>token</code>对象，每个<code>token</code>对象又包含类型和内容两个属性，如果当前<code>token</code>又嵌套内容，则单独开辟第三项用于存储)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>如何实现嵌套循环？</strong></p>
<p>引入栈和收集器(<code>collector</code>)，一开始，让<code>collector</code>指向nestedTokens结果数组，它是一个引用类型值，遇见#时，将当前的<code>token</code> 放入栈中，并给token添加下标为2的项，并且让<code>collector</code>指向它：<code>collector = token[2] = []</code>,遇见/时，先将栈顶元素退栈，此时改变<code>collector</code>为栈顶元素下标为2的数组，如果栈顶此时无元素，则证明当前的嵌套循环以及完成闭合或者无嵌套，可以让<code>collector</code>重新指向结果数组<code> collector = sections.length &gt; 0 ? sections[sections.length - 1][2] : nestedTokens;</code></p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    函数的功能:折叠tokens，将#和/之间的tokens能够整合起来，作为它的下标为2的项</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"> */</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">nestTokens</span>(<span class="params">tokens</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 结果数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> nestedTokens = [];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 栈结构，存放小tokens，栈顶的tokens数组中是当前操作的小tokens数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> sections = [];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 收集器，指向nestedTokens结果数组，引用类型值</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> collector = nestedTokens;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; tokens.<span class="property">length</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> token = tokens[i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">switch</span> (token[<span class="number">0</span>]) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;#&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 向收集器中放入token</span></span><br><span class="line">                collector.<span class="title function_">push</span>(token);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 入栈</span></span><br><span class="line">                sections.<span class="title function_">push</span>(token);</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 收集器换引用对象,给token添加下标为2的项，并且让收集器指向它</span></span><br><span class="line">                collector = token[<span class="number">2</span>] = [];</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;/&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 出栈</span></span><br><span class="line">                sections.<span class="title function_">pop</span>();</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 改变收集器为栈结构队尾那项下标为2的数组,如果有多层嵌套，直接返回栈顶</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 栈顶即最新入栈的那个小section</span></span><br><span class="line">                <span class="comment">// 如果栈顶无元素，则证明当前嵌套循环已经完成闭合或者无嵌套，此时将收集器指回结果数组</span></span><br><span class="line">                collector = sections.<span class="property">length</span> &gt; <span class="number">0</span> ? sections[sections.<span class="property">length</span> - <span class="number">1</span>][<span class="number">2</span>] : nestedTokens;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                collector.<span class="title function_">push</span>(token);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> nestedTokens;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="实现renderTemplate-tokens-data-函数"><a href="#实现renderTemplate-tokens-data-函数" class="headerlink" title="实现renderTemplate(tokens, data)函数"></a>实现renderTemplate(tokens, data)函数</h3><ul>
<li><p>此时我们已经利用<code>ParseTemplateToTokens(templeteStr)</code>函数得到了<code>tokens</code>数组，现在需要结合数据<code>data</code>将<code>tokens</code>对应部分填充，最终得到dom字符串。</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>renderTemplate(tokens, data)</code>函数主要通过判断当前<code>token</code>的类型作出相应的处理，用到了两个函数：</p>
<ol>
<li><p><code>lookup()</code>：功能是将一个多层嵌套的对象属性剥离开，返回其基础数据类型(例如，<code>n.m.p=123</code>，将’.’去除，最终返回123)；</p>
</li>
<li><p><code>parseArray()</code>：功能是将’<code>#&#39;</code>和<code>&#39;/&#39;</code>之前的嵌套<code>token</code>展开并返回</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lookup <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./lookup.js&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> parseArray <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./parseArray.js&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    让tokens数组变为dom字符串</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">renderTemplate</span>(<span class="params">tokens, data</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 结果字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> resultStr = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 遍历tokens</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; tokens.<span class="property">length</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">let</span> token = tokens[i];</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 看类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (token[<span class="number">0</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;text&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 拼起来</span></span><br><span class="line">            resultStr += token[<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (token[<span class="number">0</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment">// 如果是name类型，使用lookup向深层查找它的值</span></span><br><span class="line">            resultStr += <span class="title function_">lookup</span>(data, token[<span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">if</span> (token[<span class="number">0</span>] == <span class="string">&#x27;#&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            resultStr += <span class="title function_">parseArray</span>(token, data);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// console.log(resultStr);</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> resultStr;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<ul>
<li><p><code>lookup()</code>函数的实现：将当前字符串中的’.’去除并保存新字符串中，依次向下获取，直到返回基础数据类型</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    在dataObj对象中，寻找用连续点符号的keyname属性</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">lookup</span>(<span class="params">dataObj, keyName</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 看看keyName中有没有点符号</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (keyName.<span class="title function_">indexOf</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>) != -<span class="number">1</span> &amp;&amp; keyName != <span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 如果有点符号，那么拆开</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> keys = keyName.<span class="title function_">split</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 临时变量，向下找到一个基础数据类型</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">var</span> temp = dataObj;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; keys.<span class="property">length</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            temp = temp[keys[i]];</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> temp;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> dataObj[keyName];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p><code>parseArray()</code>函数的实现：这函数要递归调用<code>renderTemplate()</code>函数，调用的次数由data决定</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> lookup <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./lookup.js&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> renderTemplate <span class="keyword">from</span> <span class="string">&quot;./renderTemplate.js&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    处理数组，结合renderTemplate实现递归</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    这函数要递归调用renderTemplate函数，调用的次数由data决定</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">*/</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">export</span> <span class="keyword">default</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title function_">parseArray</span>(<span class="params">token, data</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 得到整体数据data中这个数组要使用的部分</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> v = <span class="title function_">lookup</span>(data, token[<span class="number">1</span>]);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 结果字符串</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">var</span> resultStr = <span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 遍历v数组</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="keyword">let</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; v.<span class="property">length</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        resultStr += <span class="title function_">renderTemplate</span>(token[<span class="number">2</span>], &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            ...v[i],</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="string">&#x27;.&#x27;</span>: v[i]	<span class="comment">//此处需要单独对.进行处理</span></span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> resultStr;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h2 id="实现效果"><a href="#实现效果" class="headerlink" title="实现效果"></a>实现效果</h2><h3 id="测试用例"><a href="#测试用例" class="headerlink" title="测试用例"></a>测试用例</h3><ul>
<li><p>模板字符串</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> templateStr = <span class="string">`</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">            &lt;div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                &lt;ul&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                    &#123;&#123;#students&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                    &lt;li class=&quot;myli&quot;&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                        学生&#123;&#123;name&#125;&#125;的爱好是</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                        &lt;ol&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                            &#123;&#123;#hobbies&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                            &lt;li&gt;&#123;&#123;.&#125;&#125;&lt;/li&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                            &#123;&#123;/hobbies&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                        &lt;/ol&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                    &lt;/li&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                    &#123;&#123;/students&#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">                &lt;/ul&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">            &lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        `</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><p>数据：</p>
<figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">var</span> data = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">students</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">                &#123; <span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;小明&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;hobbies&#x27;</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;编程&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;游泳&#x27;</span>] &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">                &#123; <span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;小红&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;hobbies&#x27;</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;看书&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;弹琴&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;画画&#x27;</span>] &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">                &#123; <span class="string">&#x27;name&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;小强&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;hobbies&#x27;</span>: [<span class="string">&#x27;锻炼&#x27;</span>] &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            ]</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
<h3 id="浏览器渲染效果："><a href="#浏览器渲染效果：" class="headerlink" title="浏览器渲染效果："></a>浏览器渲染效果：</h3><p><img src="/2022/03/30/%E6%89%8B%E5%86%99%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0mustache%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E5%BC%95%E6%93%8E/mustache%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%95%88%E6%9E%9C.png" alt="mustache渲染效果"></p>
<h2 id="尾声"><a href="#尾声" class="headerlink" title="尾声"></a>尾声</h2><p>以上就是整个mustache模板引擎的简单实现，主要步骤在于利用<code>ParseTemplateToTokens(templeteStr)</code>函数将模板字符串转换为tokens，再结合data最后返回dom字符串。笔者也是刚入门前端，文笔技术皆有限，若有疏漏和错误，欢迎指出。</p>
